data.description: This lovely home is ready for new owners in the Whisperwind neighborhood of New Braunfels! With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms this home offers plenty of space for both living and entertaining. Let's be honest though: everyone needs a break from the family occasionally, and this floor plan offers an ideal situation with the primary bedroom on the lower floor and all other bedrooms upstairs. In addition to the spacious upstairs bedrooms and bathroom, a sizable landing area offers a solid play-space. Outside, the massive enclosed patio will become your new hang out spot! Positioned a minute from both the elementary and middle school this house is a great candidate for any growing family. Swing by and checkout this competitively priced home today, and be sure to grab a burger from the nearby Freiheit Country Store as you make plans to move into your new home.
